<h2>Industry-Specific PR Sites</h2>
<p>Niche press release sites reach journalists and readers who cover specific industries. A placement on an industry site often outperforms a general wire service for <a href="/blog/increase-organic-traffic/">targeted traffic</a>.</p>
<p><strong>118. <a href="https://techcrunch.com/">TechCrunch</a></strong>. Submit startup and tech product announcements. Extremely competitive but a single feature drives massive visibility.</p>
<p><strong>119. <a href="https://venturebeat.com/">VentureBeat</a></strong>. Technology and AI news. Accept pitch submissions for product launches and funding announcements.</p>
<p><strong>120. <a href="https://thenextweb.com/">The Next Web</a></strong>. Tech and startup news. Accept press releases for product launches and tech innovation stories.</p>
